descriptors.name: tensorflow_lite_micro_helloworld
descriptors.label: TensorFlow Lite Micro - Hello World
descriptors.description: This application demonstrates a model trained to replicate a sine function. The model is continuously fed with values ranging from 0 to 2pi, and the output of the model is used to control the intensity of an LED.

descriptors.name: tensorflow_lite_micro_microspeech
descriptors.label: TensorFlow Lite Micro - Micro Speech
descriptors.description: This application demonstrates a model trained to recognise the words "yes" and "no" from speech data recorded from the microphone. The detected keywords are transmitted over VCOM.
